N2  - The article discusses some editorial issues within the ?Academy of Management Journal.? Figures are presented for the number of manuscripts submitted for review and publication from July 15, 1988 to July 15, 1989. Changes within the Academy of Management's editorial board are discussed, including the resignation of James Terborg and Craig Olson. New members invited to join the board are listed including James Walsh, Stuart Youngblood, and Philip Anderson. The author expresses appreciation for several individuals who have contributed to the ?Academy of Management Journal,? including Nancy Dodd, John Fossum, and Michael Hitt. Ken Cooper is announced as the journal's new business manager.
